{"tid":1114557,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【影片流出】「獨立第三方」突擊港航辦公室　有人企圖帶走文件被制止","createTime":"2019-04-18T13:48:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-18T16:55:09.000Z","uid":79563,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3ff678e8e3f530adf53f84d3f4ac5bf5ee2fe798","tid":1114557,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T13:48:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/fin/20190417/s00010/af9635fdf8547952e2f1ff10d9c481ea.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2F20190417%2Fs00010%2Faf9635fdf8547952e2f1ff10d9c481ea.jpg&h=1cd9e31d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1555502356508&amp;issue=20190417\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1555502356508%26issue%3D20190417&d=kjYWGV%2FOxf%2BJAuwkXUN1dKNZBGycwMyv8OGD44uLuTw%3D&h=fbf8b8b3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1555502356508%26issue%3D20190417&h=93f28fc7\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1555502356508&amp;issue=20190417</a><br />\n香港航空股東內鬥再有新進展，據港航內部員工向記者爆料，昨晚曾有第三方顧問團到抵港航位於東涌的總部，打算調查公司的財務狀況，惟有人企圖帶走大量文件。<br />\n<br />\n據該名內部員工提供的片段所見，有兩名揹背包的男子企圖帶走一行李箱，據了解，行李箱內均為公司的內部文件。事發時間約為昨晚9時，地點正是位於東薈城的港航總部。顧問團向該兩男子表示「文件不能帶走」，最後該兩男子將行李箱帶返回公司辦公室內。<br />\n<br />\n港航兩控股股東「香港航空諮詢服務公司」及「Frontier Investment Partner」昨日曾發聲明，指公司有新董事會變動，並由鍾國頌擔任董事會主席，新團隊並已聘請獨立專業人士及機構對港航的財務狀況進行第三方調查及評估。惟有關的董事會變動仍未經港航官方證實。而現任港航董事兼公司主席的侯偉，今日以「主席（Chairman）」身份向員工發出內部信件，指公司董事會變動是源於股東爭拗（shareholders dispute），又強調事件不會影響公司營運。<br />\n<br />\n代表「香港航空諮詢服務公司」及「Frontier Investment Partner」的公關則向傳媒補充，昨日舉行的特別股東大會有若干法律意見支持，依足法定程序進行。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">港航正面臨嚴重的財務狀況及財務上的不當行為</span></span></strong>，控股股東有關行動旨在捍衛公司的財務穩健性，及<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">阻止進一步的關聯方交易和任何中飽私囊的行為。</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"517bab48d35156e3831d440d2684bc56c29b4cc6","tid":1114557,"uid":190540,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T13:52:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"864a5fff5fe41bbed29fae74038b58b8f05efb4d","tid":1114557,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T13:55:00.000Z","msg":"玩撚猿 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08def4f91142d63140ca562137b8f53e4b95d40b","tid":1114557,"uid":220701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T15:53:24.000Z","msg":"香港=支那"},{"pid":"d1f2f09b3c04b980b20a7a3b1220e0cf231067e1","tid":1114557,"uid":76216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T15:57:13.000Z","msg":"等清盤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fb5f8c44a210b44ab87981c0f2c03d873147bde","tid":1114557,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T16:42:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec51660b78119e530fae49388878b718d965c3f6","tid":1114557,"uid":235152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T16:48:31.000Z","msg":"有人偷公司錢做假數<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc6a9c8c99c258721532acc75519a5a21f452e3b","tid":1114557,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ec51660b78119e530fae49388878b718d965c3f6","tid":1114557,"uid":235152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T16:48:31.000Z","msg":"有人偷公司錢做假數<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T16:55:09.000Z","msg":"報ICAC啦<br />\n<br />\n真CHECK到"}]}